Skill name: Quick Draw (also known as Ikiado)
Cost: 35
Guild level: 12
Syntax: qdraw <target>

Description:
This is a talent you've practiced for many years. It's one that a
Samurai relies on - the ability to draw your sword faster then the eye
can perceive it. Using this skill, you bring your sword to your target's
throat faster then he can say 'Um.', forcing him to face his greatest
challenge - cowardice. You see, he has a choice. He can either fight
you and be free, or he can sit there (like the coward that he is).
Be aware, if he chooses to fight you, then he is no longer held.
